SUMMARY:Camas SpringFest & Egg Scramble
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a fun-filled celebration of spring with activities\, games\, and family-friendly entertainment for all ages. They’re bringing beloved traditions\, mixing in fresh fun\, and celebrating the return of sunshine\, smiles and springtime vibes. Full details and schedule will be available on the event host’s website on March 1!
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/camas-springfest-egg-scramble/
LOCATION:Crown Park\, Camas\, 120 NE 17th Ave.\, Camas\, WA\, 98607
CATEGORIES:Active,Easter,Family Fun,Kids Calendar
