SUMMARY:Lee Farms Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Bring the whole family out for an afternoon of egg hunting and farm fun! Each Egg Hunt & Activities ticket includes:\n\n\n\nA hunt for 12 eggs to trade for age-appropriate prizes\nFrolic in an egg field perfect for photos\nTime to play on the bounce pad\, slides\, hay maze & enjoy barrel wagon rides\nA take-home sugar cookie with buttercream frosting & sprinkles\nVisits with friendly farm animals like goats\, rabbits\, pigs\, donkeys & more!\n\n\nStart Times: 10:00 AM · 11:00 AM · 12:00 PM · 1:00 PM\n\nPRICE DETAILS\nAdult/Non-Hunter Tickets: $5 Each\nEgg Hunt and Activities Tickets: $18 Each\n\n\nGet your tickets here:\nleefarms.ticketspice.com/2026-lee-farms-easter-egg-hunt\n\n\nWant some extra morning fun? Go early for breakfast with the Easter Bunny (tix required)!
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/lee-farms-easter-egg-hunt/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:Lee Farms
CATEGORIES:Active,Animals,Easter,Family Fun,Farm,Kids Calendar,Outdoor
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Easter-Egg-Hunt-at-Lee-Farms.jpg
END:VEVENT
