SUMMARY:Garcia Birthday Band @ Sanctuary Hall
DESCRIPTION:Garcia Birthday Band\, based in Portland Oregon\, isn’t your mother’s Grateful Dead cover band. Playing for over 25 years\, GBB has evolved into something far deeper than the sum of its parts. The beating heart of the Pacific Northwest’s GD community\, the band’s ever-expanding fanbase is an experience unto themselves.\n\nJoin us for an incredibly special evening as GBB takes acoustic sanctuary in one of the most beautiful hidden gems in Portland. Reflect\, dance\, and heal with us as we channel our collective joy into something larger than ourselves. \nAll ages \nUnder 18 FREE\, (but still requires a ticket). 18 and up – $20. \nFull bar on site \nADA Accessible \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/garcia-birthday-band-sanctuary-hall/
LOCATION:Sanctuary Hall at First Congretional\, 1126 SW Park Ave\, Portland\, Oregon\, 97205
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Kids Calendar,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/biopic.jpg
END:VEVENT
