SUMMARY:Lee Farms Breakfast with the Easter Bunny
DESCRIPTION:Before you collect your eggs for the day\, frolic in the field for pictures\, and play on our wonderful activities – join them for breakfast! The Easter Bunny will be doing photo ops and meet & greets during breakfast as well. \nPRICE DETAILS\nAdult Tickets: $35 Each\nChildren’s Tickets: $35 Each\nEvery attendee 1 and up MUST have a ticket to join the breakfast and egg hunts. \n🗓️ Dates: March 28th\, March 29th\n⏰Time Slots: 8:00AM\, 8:30AM\, 9:00AM\, or 9:30AM\n🥚Egg hunt and all open farm activities included in ticket!!\n🎁Each child gets a gift from the farm!\n🐰Meet & Greet with Easter Bunny\n🧡Mimosas available for purchase with breakfast!\n👥You will be seated with your group\, if you are meeting more friends & family please all gather together and check in together.\n🏠8am seating in Greenhouse\, 9am seating in Grain Bin\n🍴Assortment of Lee Farms Donuts & Pastries\, French Toast\, Pancakes\, Eggs\, Bacon\, Sausage\, Yogurt & Fruit\, Juice\, Hot Cocoa & House Coffee
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/lee-farms-breakfast-with-the-easter-bunny/2026-03-29/
