DESCRIPTION:Bridgeport Village Scavenger Hunt\nwith Mike Bennett Studios\nMarch 15 – April 5 | during center hours\nStroll through Bridgeport Village to find all 12 hidden springtime flowers and bugs created by local artist Mike Bennett. \nStart your search by picking up a scavenger hunt checklist at the Security Office (located between Madewell and Barnes & Noble). \nOnce you’ve found all 12 characters\, return your completed checklist to the Security Office to claim a prize!* \nThis scavenger hunt is perfect for little ones — and a fun way to explore Bridgeport Village. \n*Limit one prize per child\, while supplies last. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
